fields.name: Roe Wine
fields.description: Taking fashion to new heights, this high-low homecoming dress is an irresistible choice. Lace applique stylishly decorates the off-shoulder bodice with floral patterns, and rhinestones add a sparkle. A bow-sash tops layers of tulle that form tiers and finish with fashionable horsehair hemlines.

fields.name: Kellindra Black
fields.description: A stunning A-line silhouette, along with a captivating lace bodice and a dramatic asymmetrical satin skirt, makes this beautiful evening dress shine. Slip into this fabulous dress with statement jewellery and strappy heels to exude perfection all the way.

fields.name: Brielle
fields.description: Be like a princess when you wear this splendid long ball-gown prom dress. This dazzling gown features a romantic sweetheart neckline that is highlighted by sparkling beads. The beautiful lace, adorned with shining sequins, cascades over the tulle bodice that creates a gorgeous look.

fields.name: Gibson Sandals
fields.description: Gold Leatherette Stiletto Heel Sandals Pumps Peep Toe.

fields.name: Haisley
fields.description: Green Leatherette Stiletto Heel Sandals Pumps Peep Toe With Buckle shoes.

fields.name: Kristina
fields.description: Sleek and sophisticated, the Kristina clutch bag features a removable chain link strap, allowing you to switch up your look from occasion to occasion - choosing to drape it over your shoulder or go for a chic hand-held style. Flap over front. Detachable chain strap.

fields.name: Colour Elixir by Clinique
fields.description: Colour Elixir Lipstick is specifically developed to give rich colour and moisture in one swipe that lasts up to 24 hours. It contains a blend of 60% emollients, conditioners & antioxidants including vitamin E. It's comfortable to wear, feels lightweight and glides on smoothly & evenly.

fields.name: Rachael Red
fields.description: Wide fit red court shoes. Holds all the hallmarks of the classic court shoe. Elegant stiletto heel. Pointed toe.

fields.name: Bold Berries Lipstick
fields.description: Looking for a lip colour that really makes a statement? Say anything and everything with our new Bold Berries Lipstick. This is not just another bullet lipstick, with one swipe application that is so highly pigmented it looks the same on all lip colours this is an absolute must try to revoluntionise your lipstick game. Its pigment-packed formula loads lips with intense, rich colour and delivers up to four hours of hydration in just one swipe.

fields.name: Crème Bronzer
fields.description: Who says you can/’t have a natural, sun-kissed glow all year round? Our rule-breaking makeup artistry brings you the Bronzer to create a natural glow any time of year. Formula ultra-blendable, streak-free formula with baked minerals for a natural, sun-kissed glow. Micro-fine pigments and multi-tonal shades blend effortlessly with skin tones. Simply buff the bronzer sparingly across your face, gradually building depth and colour until you achieve the desired effect. The multi-tonal shades are designed to enhance and flatter your natural features for a radiant golden glow. Size: 3g.

fields.name: Emily necklace
fields.description: Material Type: Alloy, rhinestones, imitation pearls. Necklace Closure Type: Lobster Clasp. Length of Necklace: 45cm.

fields.name: Balenciaga Pouch
fields.description: Navy pouch with strap in beige cotton canvas and black calfskin. Contrasted leather frame. Removable strap. 2 compartments and 1 zipped pocket inside. Dimensions: W 26cm H 19cm D 6.5cm. Composition: 43% Cotton, 43% Linen, 10% Calfskin, 4% Polyurethane.

fields.name: Beaverbrooks Sapphire
fields.description: Crafted with an 18ct white gold polished band. A deep blue sapphire stone glistens at the heart of the ring. Glittering halo of round brilliant diamonds. Round brilliant diamonds fall beautifully down the shoulders. Diamond cut: round brilliant. Diamond colour: G. Diamond clarity: Si1. Diamond carat weight: 0.20ct. Size: J.

fields.name: Beaverbrooks Platinum
fields.description: This gorgeous diamond cluster ring is fit for a princess. Crafted with a polished platinum band for the most rare, pure and eternal finish. Carefully hand selected cluster of round brilliant diamonds to form a drop shape. Diamond cut: round brilliant. Diamond colour: G. Diamond clarity: Si1. Diamond carat weight: 0.80ct. Size: M.

fields.name: Daisy Love
fields.description: Addictive and irresistible. This gourmand radiant perfume reveals its first notes in a vibrant burst of sweet cloudberries. Delicate daisy tree petals mingle with sparkling cashmere musks and driftwood to create a lasting and memorable gourmand twist. Top notes: Raspberry, cloudberry. Heart notes: Cream, Daisy. Base notes: Driftwood, Musk. Scent: Floral. Size: 50ml

fields.name: Gabrielle Chanel
fields.description: A floral, solar and voluptuous interpretation composed by Olivier Polge, perfumer-creator for the House of Chanel. Before it was the name of a fragrance, Gabrielle was the name of a woman: Coco Chanel. A woman who made history by changing the rules. A woman, passionate and free, who always chose to be the person she wanted to be. To wear Gabrielle Chanel is to reveal your own intensity, to follow your own path and feel radiant and alive. Size: 50ml.

fields.name: YSL envelope
fields.description: Saint Laurent monogram envelope bag with a front flap and magnetic snap closure, decorated with metal YSL initials and a mix of vertical, chevron and quilted overstitching, featuring a leather and chain strap. Dimensions 21x13x6cm. 100% calfskin leather. Grosgrain lining. Interior: One main compartment, one flat pocket. Exterior: One flat pocket at the back. Shoulder strap drop: 55cm.

fields.name: Versace Eros
fields.description: Love, passion, beauty and desire: these are the key concepts of the men/’s fragrance by Versace. Eros, God of Love, able to make people fall in love with his bow and arrow. A luminous aura with an intense, vibrant and glowing freshness obtained from the combination of mint leaves, Italian lemon zest and green apple. An addictive sensuality delivered by oriental, intriguing and enveloping notes like Tonka beans, Ambroxan (amber), Geranium flower and vanilla. Top notes: Mint, Lemon, Apple. Base notes: Vanilla, Vetyver, Oak Moss, Cedarwood. Heart notes: Tonka Bean, Ambroxan, Geranium Flower. Size: 50ml.

fields.name: Chanel Le Vernis
fields.description: A shiny, high-coverage nail polish that remains gentle on the nails with a thin brush for precise application. Featuring an ergonomic cap for easy use and a no-spill bottle. A bioceramic-based active ingredient, phycocoral, delivers calcium, iron, zinc and magnesium to the nails to strengthen them. Ceramides to help hydrate the nails. With high concentration of pigments for an intense lacquered result. Formula enriched with a cotton-derived resin for a sheer, shiny and resilient coat of colour. Size 13ml.

fields.name: Prada Cahier
fields.description: Made of calf leather, it is defined by the metal hardware decorating the front and shoulder strap. Detachable metal chain shoulder strap. Metal hardware. Metal lettering logo. Strap closure on the front. Inside pocket. Leather lining in a contrasting color. 11.5cm in height, 4cm in length and 18cm in width
